31 Aug 2017 01:16






The info of the drivers in question isn't actually stored in the apps' databases, so rating them down doesn't have any effect. Getting a 5-star rating doesn't turn you into one of the drivers; it's the mechanism by which they attract riders. I updated the containment procedures to make it clear that only the  5-star drivers are anomalous and to be contained.







